        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2\n\nwe use staging repositories to build our daily release where candidate release versions are available : look in Nexus staging repository group, you'll see that the release artifact exist already : /org/openecomp/mso/libs/openstack-java-sdk/1.1.0/openstack-java-sdk-1.1.0.pom",
